title: SDMS Kepala Batas F.C.
text:
Sinar Dimaja Maisara Navy Kepala Batas Football Club also known as SDM Navy Kepala Batas FC is a <a href="Malaysia">Malaysia</a>n <a href="Association%20football">football</a> club formerly playing in <a href="Malaysia%20FAM%20League">Malaysia FAM League</a>. The club is based in <a href="Kepala%20Batas%2C%20Penang">Kepala Batas</a>, <a href="Penang">Penang</a>, <a href="Malaysia">Malaysia</a>. In 2013, the club has pulled from the league for financial reasons.
